{"tid":1990829,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"明明仲愛對方 點解唔可以一齊返","createTime":"2020-04-27T04:00:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-28T12:24:23.000Z","uid":199574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1db3caa3b0ffef2be143fea6c8511d0b8152e8ba","tid":1990829,"uid":199574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T04:00:46.000Z","msg":"近日我有事入左ICU 到依兩日醒返<br />\n琴晚打左個電話比佢<br />\n我問左一句 我地之間係咪得返朋友既關心<br />\n佢疾左幾秒 聽到電話另一頭有喊聲<br />\n佢答我 唔係<br />\n我再問佢 咁我地有冇得係返埋一齊<br />\n佢答我 唔知<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好苦<br />\n我可以點做"},{"pid":"fa2b395f8f3367459a58f3636b0254cd814d3700","tid":1990829,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T04:02:55.000Z","msg":"可唔可以detail少少<br />\n入ICU之前係點<br />\n你講到好似因為你入左ICU<br />\n佢就唔要你咁<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">聽到電話另一頭有喊聲</span><br />\n唔明 即係佢有第二個?<br />\n而佢第二個聽到你係ICU所以喊?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f48227095e861f0f84a3e91f12a3ea4a748e96c1","tid":1990829,"uid":2772,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T04:04:58.000Z","msg":"佢會咁 係因為分開佢都辛苦<br />\n至於點解唔會係返埋一齊<br />\n係因為一齊返仲辛苦過分開"},{"pid":"30b14fcd7623bcd6fd016b8d3869029111b6a5e5","tid":1990829,"uid":52539,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T04:27:46.000Z","msg":"呢個位好重要 錯過左就冇 千萬不要鬥氣<br />\n<br />\n你唔可以交哂個波比佢 <br />\n你個立場要同佢企埋同一陣線 主動解決個問題<br />\n<br />\n你脆弱煩惱時 對方都一樣<br />\n當覺得自己冇力解決既時候 唯有揀放棄<br />\n所以你要做既係 用佢既立場 主動同佢一齊諗 <br />\n而唔係期望對方安慰自己<br />\n對方先會覺得你有心 愛佢 明佢 感性同理性咁解決問題"},{"pid":"5b2a71eb5dd2230a86bc7e86e38d7d8e3a3dfd0f","tid":1990829,"uid":293845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f48227095e861f0f84a3e91f12a3ea4a748e96c1","tid":1990829,"uid":2772,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T04:04:58.000Z","msg":"佢會咁 係因為分開佢都辛苦<br />\n至於點解唔會係返埋一齊<br />\n係因為一齊返仲辛苦過分開"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T08:01:05.000Z","msg":"同意"},{"pid":"9fef6bcbd9b8cbcec5dd7e6246f0e7f48c478871","tid":1990829,"uid":247940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f48227095e861f0f84a3e91f12a3ea4a748e96c1","tid":1990829,"uid":2772,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T04:04:58.000Z","msg":"佢會咁 係因為分開佢都辛苦<br />\n至於點解唔會係返埋一齊<br />\n係因為一齊返仲辛苦過分開"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T08:11:30.000Z","msg":"I know that feel <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75f4edb9cabe36bf404164dc8280c2497891b04f","tid":1990829,"uid":54246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T12:24:23.000Z","msg":"我都係，我仲鍾意佢，但都無一齊返<br />\n因為有d問題解決唔到咪長痛不如短痛"}]}